content.text:
Here's the diff preview of the changes I'll make to the CSS:

## CSS Changes for `.report-nav-bar` and related styles:

```css
/* CURRENT */
.report-nav-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: #1F2937;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}

/* UPDATED */
.report-nav-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 792px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    padding: 0;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #1a1a1a, #000000);
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* UPDATED nav-segment */
.nav-segment {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 16px;
    height: 100%;
}

/* Add divider after segments */
.nav-segment:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 1px;
    height: 18px;
    background-color: #4B5563;
}

/* Update label and value colors */
.nav-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #bec2c6;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
}

.nav-value {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    min-width: auto;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
}

/* Update bureau logo */
.bureau-logo {
    height: 24px;
    width: auto;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
}

/* Update nav arrows to be circular */
.nav-arrows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-left: 8px;
}

.nav-arrow-small {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid #4B5563;
    color: #9CA3AF;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 50%;
}

.nav-arrow-small:hover {
    background-color: rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.3);
    border-color: #6B7280;
    color: #FFFFFF;
}

.nav-arrow-small i {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
}
```

