## CSS Changes Preview:

### 1. Background Container Changes:
```css
/* Add master background container */
.vioverse-app {
    position: relative;
    width: 1920px;
    height: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #4f5a63; /* 70% tint of #253541 */
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* Update body to center the app */
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #2a2a2a; /* Darker than app background for contrast */
}
```

### 2. Nav Bar Updates:
```css
.report-nav-bar {
    position: absolute;
    left: 369px;
    top: 80px;
    width: 792px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: #253541;
    border: 3px solid #9ba1a6; /* 30% tint of #253541 */
    border-radius: 36px;
    box-shadow: none;
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* Update arrow and divider colors */
.nav-arrow-small {
    color: #9ba1a6; /* 30% tint */
}

.nav-arrow-small:hover {
    color: #253541; /* Full color on hover */
}

.nav-divider {
    background-color: #9ba1a6; /* 30% tint */
}

.nav-label {
    color: #9ba1a6; /* 30% tint */
}
```

### 3. Report Canvas Container:
```css
.report-canvas-container {
    position: absolute;
    left: 360px;
    top: 129px; /* 69px + 60px to account for nav bar height and spacing */
    width: 810px;
    height: 920px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.report-canvas {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
}

.report-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
}
```

### 4. Content Structure Updates:
```css
/* Hide or adjust other UI elements for full-screen experience */
.main-nav,
.docket-header {
    display: none; /* Or position them differently */
}

.main-content {
    position: static;
    background: transparent;
}

.content-wrapper {
    position: static;
    display: block;
}
```

